<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id4d47b659-5dcd-11f1-b11b-9e551e93f87d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s3716a">section 3716a of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
